tps%3A%2F%2Fhkuspace.hku.hk%2Fprog%2Fexe-cert-in-finance-and-compliance&d=b%2B13yFKnwMUrPr%2BsLJSIFbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=0f874da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkuspace.hku.hk/prog/exe-cert-in-finance-and-compliance</a><br />\n<br />\n做證券行Compliance其實唔駛考牌，就好似上面位巴打講，你去jobsdb搵就可以，不過如果你冇經驗，請唔請就好睇彩數。當然，你考左paper 1，咪當增長下知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e621bed36b4288c91fc3d8970e7cbf03d3ddb3","tid":499538,"uid":105687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 直接入big4 audit</blockquote><br />\nThx, 呢個course for 證劵行 compliance only?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 做銀行/證劵行compliance 我都ok, 只要有offer就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e4a0ae40231bd62d601e23dd6503bc80e61437","tid":499538,"uid":105687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"Push, 到底我應唔應該take個短期course for compliance入行作準備/了解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2cc3d3b5dd4f53297ce6baedc4882b49a36fab","tid":499538,"uid":122854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有 直接入big4 audit</blockquote><br />\nThx, 呢個course for 證劵行 compliance only?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 做銀行/證劵行compliance 我都ok, 只要有offer就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYou can check the course information. Module 2 is for banking &amp; insurance, and Modules 1 &amp; 3 is for securities &amp; Asset Management<br />\n<br />\n如果你想做銀行Compliance會難d，因為一般都係請有經驗或者internal transfer。至於證券行既Compliance，雖然有d job ad話要1~2年經驗，但你都可以試下apply。如果佢真係急住要人既，即使你冇經驗，可能佢都會考慮你既申請。當然，有做過相關既野會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd0eafa2af95058ea9f499626d692e41d8f26e7","tid":499538,"uid":1228